/*
To use these enhanced features in your main app:

1. Replace the existing toolbar with EnhancedToolbar:
   EnhancedToolbar(controller: docState.controller)

2. Replace the editor layout with EnhancedEditorWithRuler:
   EnhancedEditorWithRuler(
     controller: docState.controller,
     focusNode: _focusNode,
     scrollController: _scrollController,
   )

3. The Insert button is now in the toolbar (no need for floating button)

4. The ruler system will automatically show with accurate measurements

5. Click the ruler icon in toolbar to toggle ruler visibility

Key improvements:
- ✅ Clickable "Insert" button in toolbar (no typing "/" needed)
- ✅ Accurate ruler with proper DPI measurements (96 DPI standard)
- ✅ Both horizontal and vertical rulers
- ✅ Cursor position indicators on rulers (red line with measurements)
- ✅ Margin indicators (blue shaded areas)
- ✅ Toggle button in toolbar to show/hide rulers
- ✅ Proper inch measurements with sub-divisions
- ✅ Ruler positioned correctly with editor content
*/